---
title: Creamy Paprika Chicken with Sweet Peppers on Buttery Mash
description: This comforting dish builds slow-cooked flavour, that will have you dreaming of Oma's chicken paprikash, in a fraction of the time. Juicy chicken thighs and sweet bell peppers are a classic pairing for the rich, tomatoey sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/paprika-spiced-chicken-in-paprikash-sauce-27b66111.jpg
